'''西蒙斯'''（{{lang-nl|Xavier Quentin Shay Simons}}，{{bd|2003年|4月21日}}）是一名荷兰足球运动员，场上司职[[中场|中场]]，現效力于[[荷兰足球甲级联赛|荷甲]]球隊[[PSV燕豪芬|PSV燕豪芬]]。


==早年==
西蒙斯出生在[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]，他的父亲是苏里南裔<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.srnieuws.com/suriname/228115/onderhandeling-voor-bondscoach-gesprongen/|title=Onderhandeling voor bondscoach gesprongen | Suriname Nieuws|website=www.srnieuws.com|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610003103/https://www.srnieuws.com/suriname/228115/onderhandeling-voor-bondscoach-gesprongen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>前荷兰足球运动员{{le|雷吉利奥·西蒙斯|Regillio Simons}}。<ref name="Goal">{{cite web |url=https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/who-xavi-simons-la-masia-wonderkid-barcelona-psg/3kdb5cyyo2581rqm1tbb2jwh2 |title=Who is Xavi Simons? La Masia wonderkid who broke Barcelona hearts to join PSG |date=2019-07-24 |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=goal.com |archive-date=2019-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725122001/https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/who-xavi-simons-la-masia-wonderkid-barcelona-psg/3kdb5cyyo2581rqm1tbb2jwh2 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

==俱乐部生涯==

===巴塞罗那===
西蒙斯在2010年加入了[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]的青训。有媒体称，[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英超]]豪门[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切尔西]]想要将其招入自家青训。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/2606115-chelsea-monitor-12-year-old-barcelona-starlet-xavi-simons |title=Chelsea Following the Progress of 12-Year-Old Barcelona Starlet Xavi Simons |date=2016-01-08 |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=bleacherreport.com |archive-date=2017-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207114820/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2606115-chelsea-monitor-12-year-old-barcelona-starlet-xavi-simons/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/2608341-real-madrid-transfer-news-xavi-simons-plan-reported-to-strike-back-at-ban |title=Real Madrid Transfer News: Xavi Simons Plan Reported to 'Strike Back' at Ban |date=2016-01-16 |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=bleacherreport.com |archive-date=2016-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319072821/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2608341-real-madrid-transfer-news-xavi-simons-plan-reported-to-strike-back-at-ban |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

=== 巴黎圣日耳曼 ===
2019年7月，西蒙斯[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]，[[法国足球甲级联赛|法甲]][[巴黎圣日耳曼|巴黎圣日耳曼]]的青训。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.espn.co.uk/football/soccer-transfers/story/3905165/barca-lose-dutch-youngster-xavi-simons-to-psg |title=Barca lose Dutch youngster Xavi Simons to PSG |date=2019-07-23 |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=espn.co.uk |archive-date=2019-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208153037/https://www.espn.co.uk/football/soccer-transfers/story/3905165/barca-lose-dutch-youngster-xavi-simons-to-psg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.besoccer.com/new/simons-explains-his-barca-exit-everyone-dreams-about-messi-but-725772 |title=Simons explains his Barca exit: "Everyone dreams about Messi, but..." |date=2019-10-13 |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=besoccer.com |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610003106/https://www.besoccer.com/new/simons-explains-his-barca-exit-everyone-dreams-about-messi-but-725772 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 有报道称，他的年薪将会达到100万[[欧元|欧元]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.givemesport.com/1492246-xavi-simons-is-on-1-millionperyear-at-paris-saintgermain |title=Xavi Simons is on €1 million-per-year at Paris Saint-Germain |date=2019-07-25 |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=givemesport.com |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822170539/https://www.givemesport.com/1492246-xavi-simons-is-on-1-millionperyear-at-paris-saintgermain |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年8月5日，西蒙斯在[[巴黎圣日耳曼|巴黎圣日耳曼]]1-0小胜[[索肖足球俱乐部|索肖]]的友谊赛中完成了他非正式的职业队首秀。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=La 'perla' Xavi Simons debuta con el PSG|url=https://www.marca.com/futbol/liga-francesa/2020/08/06/5f2b35ad46163fb0bf8b4604.html|access-date=2020-08-05|website=马卡报|language=es|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928060201/https://www.marca.com/futbol/liga-francesa/2020/08/06/5f2b35ad46163fb0bf8b4604.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年2月10日，在[[巴黎圣日耳曼|巴黎圣日耳曼]]客场1-0小胜[[卡昂足球俱乐部|卡昂]]的[[法国杯|法国杯]]第6轮比赛中，西蒙斯替补出场，换下了[[尤利安·德拉克斯勒|德拉克斯勒]]，完成了一线队首秀。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Caen vs. Paris Saint-Germain - Football Match Summary - February 10, 2021 - ESPN|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match?gameId=592258|access-date=2021-02-10|website=ESPN.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211005422/https://www.espn.com/soccer/match?gameId=592258|dead-url=no}}</ref>2个月后，在巴黎圣日耳曼4-1大胜[[斯特拉斯堡竞赛会|斯特拉斯堡]]的[[法国足球甲级联赛|法甲]]比赛中，西蒙斯替补登场，换下了[[安德尔·埃雷拉|埃雷拉]]，完成了法甲首秀。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Strasbourg vs. PSG - 10 April 2021 - Soccerway|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2021/04/10/france/ligue-1/racing-club-de-strasbourg/paris-saint-germain-fc/3287714/|deadurl=no|access-date=2021-04-10|website=Soccerway|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507150612/https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2021/04/10/france/ligue-1/racing-club-de-strasbourg/paris-saint-germain-fc/3287714/}}</ref>
==国家队生涯==
[[File:Lens_-_PSG_(10-09-2020)_26.jpg|thumb]]对[[朗斯足球俱乐部|朗斯U19]]的比赛中]]
西蒙斯代表过[[荷兰国家足球队|荷兰]]的U-15、U-16、以及U-17国家队参加国际比赛。<ref name="Goal"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.uefa.com/under17/teams/players/250128451--xavi-simons/ |title=Xavi Simons |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=uefa.com |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610003109/https://www.uefa.com/under17/teams/players/250128451--xavi-simons/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==个人生活==
2020年3月，他被[[Goal.com|进球网]]评为“下一代-2020”成员之一，也就是世界上最有潜力的50名足球新星。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.goal.com/en-gb/lists/nxgn-2020-the-50-best-wonderkids-in-football/1csxnxdsuupje1kjm3bu4gce8m#9w5fyeqvf56y1ce27l0g5kjhj|title=NxGn 2020: The 50 best wonderkids in football|website=goal.com|date=2020-03-31|access-date=2020-07-08|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206185949/https://www.goal.com/en-gb/lists/nxgn-2020-the-50-best-wonderkids-in-football/1csxnxdsuupje1kjm3bu4gce8m#9w5fyeqvf56y1ce27l0g5kjhj|dead-url=no}}</ref>

西蒙斯也曾被[[卫报|卫报]]评为“下一代2020”之中。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/ng-interactive/2020/oct/08/next-generation-2020-60-of-the-best-young-talents-in-world-football |title=Next Generation 2020: 60 of the best young talents in world football |date=2020-10-08 |access-date=2020-10-09 |work=卫报 |archive-date=2021-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210521100625/https://www.theguardian.com/football/ng-interactive/2020/oct/08/next-generation-2020-60-of-the-best-young-talents-in-world-football |dead-url=no }}</ref>

西蒙斯在社交媒体[[Instagram|Instagram]]上有着超过270万名关注者。他也与运动用品制造商[[耐克|耐克]]签订了赞助合同。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2019/11/13/sport/xavi-simons-prodigy-intl-spt/index.html |title=Xavi Simons: The Dutch soccer prodigy with two million Instagram followers |date=2019-11-13 |access-date=2020-05-06 |website=cnn.com |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211111016/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/11/13/sport/xavi-simons-prodigy-intl-spt/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

